snippet.textDisplay:
I tried everything but it seems so difficult. be it efforts in terms physicaly, mentaly Or financially but I can't make my dad love me... I am failing dad, world is tough place to be atleast talk to me. 

I have been let down for so long by my dad that I have started believing that there is something wrong with me, I get hurt every time but still teri Laadki mai chodungi naa tera hath.. This line means a lot to me I have been in one sided relationship with my dad for so long that now I'm okay with the fact that somehow it's working.
